Blue's Freestyle / We Family 13. ManyFacedGod (feat. James Blake) 4:44 is the fourteenth studio album and thirteenth solo album by American rapper Jay-Z. It was released on June 30, 2017 through Roc Nation. The album is solely produced by No ID with additional production from Jay-Z. Songs from the album feature Frank Ocean, Damian Marley, and Gloria Carter, Jay-Zs mother. https://extraimage.net/image/NCIn
